('lookback',
 'Lookback',
 'Moderated and unmoderated user interview platform for capturing rich qualitative research sessions',
 'Lookback is a user research platform built for conducting and capturing high-quality moderated and unmoderated interview sessions. For moderated research, Lookback provides a video call environment where the researcher watches a participant use a website, app, or prototype in real time, can annotate moments during the session, and sees the participant''s screen, face, and audio simultaneously. The participant experience is seamless - they join via a link without installing software. For unmoderated research, participants complete tasks independently while Lookback records their screen, voice, and camera, with the researcher reviewing sessions asynchronously. The platform is designed for research quality: high-resolution recordings, reliable capture even on slower connections, and a structured tagging and note-taking system for analysis. Lookback supports both remote and in-person research modes, making it flexible for a variety of study formats. The highlight reel feature allows researchers to compile key moments from multiple sessions into a short evidence video that can be shared with stakeholders who were not present. Lookback integrates with research repositories including Dovetail and EnjoyHQ, as well as calendar and scheduling tools for participant management. It is used by UX research teams who conduct high-stakes, high-quality research sessions where the nuance of participant reactions and the depth of moderated probing are essential to the research questions being investigated.',
 NULL,
 'https://lookback.io',
 'https://lookback.io',
